<h1>Accelerated Spanish Immersion Study Guatemala</h1><p>&nbsp;Casa Xelajú offers an accelerated Spanish immersion program in Quetzaltenango, Guatemala, designed for students who have limited time but want to learn intensively. This program allows participants to complete the content of the regular four- or eight-week Spanish courses in a shorter period of three or six weeks. It is suitable for beginner, intermediate, and advanced learners, with four levels available, and follows the proficiency guidelines established by the American Council on the Teaching of Foreign Languages.</p>
